episodes.title: I Can't Believe I'm Not Dead: Executive Vice President and Author Kendra Petty
episodes.description: The ConvHERsation welcomes Kendra Petty. Kendra is a woman who has succeeded in an all-male industry, becoming an Executive Vice President at two firms in the Parking Industry. Kendra is a dynamic public speaker, powerful negotiator, and dealmaker. In this episode, we discuss her rise up the corporate ladder, and how she came to write her memoir, I Can't Believe I'm Not Dead. Throughout her life, she has experienced an unimaginable amount of trauma and tragedy. Have you ever wanted to give up? Kendra has, but she didn't. She overcame insurmountable odds and created a life she loves. Keep going, and don't quit. Tune in as we talk to her about how she became a successful business woman in a male dominated industry, escaped murder, and her interactions with Snoop Dogg. Follow the ConvHERsation!
